# Netflix Clone UI and Functionality Improvements

## 2026-03-08: UI enhancements and functionality addition
- Changed the main background to `#141414` (Netflix's actual background color).
- Improved Navbar to fade into a solid background instead of transparent black.
- Enhanced the hero section with a nicer gradient and added a mock "Volume Control" button.
- Re-designed the Movie Cards to scale up on hover and display details in a more Netflix-accurate UI (including Play, Add to List, Like buttons).
- Added slider buttons (left and right arrows) to scroll the movie rows horizontally, similar to true Netflix experience.
- Implemented JS state to toggle "My List" icon (plus to checkmark) and "Like" icon (empty to solid).
- Improved the footer to better match modern streaming platforms.
- General typography and spacing adjustments.
